	(text "Clock: 14.318 OSC -> /2 (U15) & /3 (U16) -> SPEED_SEL mux (U17) -> CLK_SRC mux (U18, PIO override) -> buffer (U19) -> bus CLK. CLK sensed back to Pico via U8 (CLK_S). /3 preset per cpu_core."
